She glanced around the room.  She lowered her head.  She thought of 
Chordate.  So far, he was the only male she showed trust with.  She 
was starting to miss him a bit.

She looked up and asked again,"Where is the CR chamber?"
Noting that Arcangel and Hotrod had left, she showed a little more at 
easy with less males in the room.
